{"tid":428360,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"攔車阻路：惡男女遭起底 為人師表及人母 E-mail 此主題給朋友","createTime":"2017-10-08T04:18:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-08T06:34:19.000Z","uid":34252,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f8c8f428a2e44f43d10622c6064aa24a26ee24e6","tid":428360,"uid":34252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T04:18:01.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=Gp3N7XiJnKaECqdxuxeLTL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=274c19a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】昨晚在銅鑼灣攔巴士的惡男女，被網民揭出兩人身份，姓王男子任職補習老師，開辦小型補習社，姓伍女子則已為人母，育有一名年幼女兒，兩人過往有不少「出位」舉動，今年6月曾經一起出席立法會教育事務委員會就小三基本能力評估（BCA，前稱TSA）的公聽會，伍當場將撕毀TSA試卷，王則亂撒溪錢。<br />\n<br />\n一周後，BCA英文科筆試開考，伍帶同女兒，與王一起到有份參與考試的嘉諾撒聖家學校（九龍塘）門外抗議，遭校方職員勸阻仍未肯離開，更當場放火燒試卷，最終驚動警方及消防到場，勞煩消防將火救熄，他們的激進行為惹來各界批評，被指「搞事攞威」及「教壞細路」。網民亦對兩人今次的行為深感不齒，紛紛批評：「咁嘅人都可以為人師表？」、「完全係誤人子弟！」、「我諗無人想自己嘅仔女畀佢教！」、「點樣做人父母？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個2條仆街真係好過火 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7kWyjViXZy0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7kWyjViXZy0&d=Gp3N7XiJnKaECqdxuxeLTL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=2147fc71\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7kWyjViXZy0</a>"},{"pid":"69bab746a76935cad8d0c3482b0e8e17a69da6aa","tid":428360,"uid":34252,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T04:19:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/TUdm18UR3em86F3XaBu2kA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/onccinstantnews.com/e714314d83bba980a23d52d5ea07bac4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FTUdm18UR3em86F3XaBu2kA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2Fe714314d83bba980a23d52d5ea07bac4&h=ee7e449f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1981958623051e645ff068e5f195dc2f8fe85cf","tid":428360,"uid":71